data.description: Stunning, single family at end of cul-de-sac, views of canal. This home has beautiful high ceilings, tile . The community is a 55plus  gated and manned. There is a community pool for your enjoyment. The home has accordion shutters throughout. Brand New Solar System By Sunpower. A/C and water heated one year old . Brand new plaza with Publix ,Starbucks, Chipotle, Gas station and more 4 minutes away. 15 minutes from the Beach . Two car garage and 6 car driveway for your Guest
